{"type": "article", "id": 5202, "title": "Slims 系列灯具", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-14T07:39:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606135235heUnfGSxmjCgzkXw.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自以色列特拉维夫的设计工作室 Studio Beam ，以设计和制作高端工具而闻名。全新推出的 Slims 系列主打细长且棱角锐利的造型，分为 Slim Billy-bob, Slim Ellie-Mae, Slim Floyd, Slim Elmo 与 Slim Rufus 五款。设计团队希望借由最简单的设计语言传达工业美感，采用激光切割金属技术和焊接技术制造这一系列的灯具，内部灯泡的光线透过外部的金属条线结构向外扩散，实为一款工业感十足的复古灯具。定价 2380 以色列新谢克尔（约合人民币 3746 元），<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/il-en/listing/180971192/black-slim-floyd-pendant-size-40x31-cm?ref=shop_home_active_12\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135233xid6DtWasG52nmMC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061352339KjwgrBtYZ0MN5Td.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135234MVyi2DgAYqLGd4zQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135234TVrPO3yFo7vkXxn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8328125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135235iUFP6aMyr8fTowph.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}